flowchart TD
    subgraph Cluster Topology
        subgraph Zone A
            NodeA1[Node worker-01]
            NodeA2[Node worker-02]
        end
        subgraph Zone B
            NodeB1[Node worker-03]
            NodeB2[Node worker-04]
        end
    end

    Pod1[Web Pod 1] -->|Scheduled| NodeA1
    
    subgraph New Pod Placement Decision
        Pod2[Web Pod 2] -->|Anti-Affinity Rule: Match app=web, topologyKey: hostname| NodeA1
    end
    
    NodeA1 -->|Has Pod 1 with label app=web| RejectA1[Reject Node worker-01]
    Pod2 -->|Evaluates worker-02| NodeA2
    NodeA2 -->|No app=web pod running| AcceptA2[Place Pod 2 here]

    subgraph High Availability Zone Spread
        Pod3[Web Pod 3] -->|Anti-Affinity Rule: Match app=web, topologyKey: zone| ZoneA[Zone A Nodes]
        ZoneA -->|Contains app=web pods| RejectZoneA[Reject Zone A]
        Pod3 -->|Evaluates Zone B Nodes| ZoneB[Zone B Nodes]
        ZoneB -->|No app=web pods running| AcceptZoneB[Place Pod 3 in Zone B]
    end
    
    style RejectA1 fill:#f43f5e,stroke:#be123c,color:#fff
    style RejectZoneA fill:#f43f5e,stroke:#be123c,color:#fff
    style AcceptA2 fill:#10b981,stroke:#047857,color:#fff
    style AcceptZoneB fill:#10b981,stroke:#047857,color:#fff
